OL,3,CScouser Lee Sandales wins Oscar for
OL,4,Cbest production design on Wicked
OL,6,FA set decorator from Liverpool has
OL,7,Ftaken home the Oscar for best
OL,8,Fproduction design for his work on
OL,9,FWicked.
OL,11,FLee Sandales accepted the award
OL,12,Falongside his collaborator, Nathan
OL,13,FCrowley, at the Dolby Theatre in
OL,14,FHollywood on Sunday 2 March.
OL,16,FLee, 53, also received a BAFTA in the
OL,17,Fproduction design category for his
OL,18,Fwork on the film ` making this Oscar
OL,19,Fhis second win for the fantasy film
OL,20,FWicked.
