OL,3,CScouser Lee Sandales wins Oscar for
OL,4,Cbest production design on Wicked
OL,6,FThe blockbuster musical, which
OL,7,Fpremiered last year, was directed by
OL,8,FJon M. Chu and is loosely based on the
OL,9,FWizard of Oz.
OL,11,FSpeaking about the achievement, Nathan
OL,12,Fsaid: "Wicked was one of our greatest
OL,13,Fexperiences of all time to make and we
OL,14,Fowe that to Jon Chu."
OL,16,FLee added: "Jon you took us over the
OL,17,Frainbow. Thanks you so much."
OL,19,FHe added: "(Thanks to) my whole team,
OL,20,Fmy family friends back home and my
OL,21,Fhusband, Mark."
