OL,6,FShe said: "I can't put into words how
OL,7,Fproud of him we are. It's easy to take
OL,8,Fcredit for him, but we just gave him
OL,9,Fthe guidance that he needed and
OL,10,Fencouraged him as a young boy for him
OL,11,Fto do what he wanted to do.
OL,13,F"The fact is, it's him. It's how hard
OL,14,Fhe's worked to make that dream come
OL,15,Ftrue as young a boy in the theatre,
OL,16,Fwho said this is what I want to do. He
OL,17,Fworked hard, studied hard and gave up
OL,18,Fa lot to be where he is now."
